{"tid":1290600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[將政權往死裏打］聽日遊行，五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T14:41:58.000Z","uid":249304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdb644216401cf94126d66a78624ce422ef58ab","tid":1290600,"uid":249304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"呢一星期可能發生左太多事失左焦<br />\n<br />\n聽日大家岀黎遊行大家要專注集中返我地初心<br />\n<br />\n就係五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n自第一次遊行以黎<br />\n<br />\n政府一直都高姿態拒絕回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府一直都比其他野去敷衍我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當我地狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一個月我地根本一事無成<br />\n<br />\n先安內而後攘外<br />\n<br />\n聽日我地以經再無餘力去理其他野<br />\n<br />\n更何況要鼓勵/支持他人，無野係比一個成功經驗更有效<br />\n<br />\n你成功左就會成為其他地方榜樣！<br />\n<br />\n聽日，我地一定要呢個腐敗政權<br />\n<br />\n再次面對佢地最不想面對既<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有暴民，只有暴政</span>"},{"pid":"36d6efe1f8b37e4139910e73989cae5742e7c5f0","tid":1290600,"uid":249304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"專注！專注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30b58d798f2b53d81ec630f4d9448277734900e","tid":1290600,"uid":249304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"推比更多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e125c32683d45ee2cd6eb75a947ece4f33e25ffa","tid":1290600,"uid":249304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}